FedShuffle with momentum variance\nreduction (Cutkosky & Orabona, 2019) improves upon non-local methods under a\nHessian similarity assumption.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Apr 2022 20:02:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Jul 2022 14:48:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 27 Sep 2022 09:42:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-28"}
