, semi-online and\nadaptive online. The adaptive online method automatically selects the fully\nonline or semi-online and can achieve a good trade-off between modeling\naccuracy and efficiency.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Apr 2022 20:26:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 8 Jan 2023 18:06:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-10"}
