k can\naccelerate the planet formation process, particularly at wide orbital\nseparations, and potentially explain planets distant from the central stars and\nyoung protoplanetary disks with substructures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Apr 2022 07:10:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-08"}
