ubling bifurcation\nwith other bifurcations. These experimental findings are confirmed by numerical\nsimulations, emphasizing both the universality of the period doubling\nbifurcations and their potentially highly complicated manifestations within\nultrafast laser systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Apr 2022 13:11:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-29"}
