od. We also give two analogues of the\nRobinson--Schensted correspondence for colored partition diagrams and, as an\napplication, we classify the equivalence classes of Green's left, right and\ntwo-sided relations for the colored partition monoid in terms of these\ncorrespondences.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Apr 2022 15:29:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 30 May 2022 08:53:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-31"}
